node.text: When then-President Donald Trump announced Operation Warp Speed, the Left doubted that he would deliver a vaccine and some even said they wouldn’t take it. Now, they’re blaming Republicans for vaccine hesitancy. TONIGHT on “Hannity,” Sen. Rand Paul, Kayleigh McEnany and Miranda Devin will discuss Operation Warp Speed and the Left’s vaccine flip-flop.

node.text: It’s been over a year since the pandemic began and we still don’t know the origin of COVID-19. For months, Democrats criticized the lab-leak theory as a right-wing conspiracy, but now they admit that COVID-19 likely originated in a lab. Joe Concha and Jason Chaffetz will discuss the validity of the lab-leak theory and why the Left took so long to acknowledge it TONIGHT on “Hannity.”
